Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.03,0:00:00.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,--------------op--------------
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.32,0:00:06.41,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}確かな想いを伝えたくて
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.85,0:00:18.23,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}戻らない時間に溺れぬように
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.62,0:00:21.97,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}今を抱きしめよう
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.12,0:00:28.85,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}その微笑みを行ったり来たり　そばにいたくて
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.06,0:00:36.56,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}この手を伸ばす　先には何が待ってるんだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.78,0:00:42.69,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}終わらない物語の向こう　飛び立て
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.93,0:00:47.50,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}本当の気持ちでたどり着く場所へと
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.74,0:00:51.49,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}心の翼を広げて
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.79,0:00:58.50,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}廻りゆくメッセージ　幸せは胸にあるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.58,0:01:02.10,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}あと少しの勇気　涙も必要なの
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.29,0:01:06.32,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}強くなれるチャンスかもね
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.45,0:01:12.92,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}温もりのリフレイン　この大切をずっと守りたい
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.01,0:01:16.69,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}心を重ねてく　絆を感じてる
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.80,0:01:20.59,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}誰も一人じゃないんだから
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.85,0:01:29.65,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}同じ空の下　確かな想いを伝えたくて
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.32,0:00:06.41,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}這份真情實感　好想將它傳遞
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.85,0:00:18.23,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}為了不沉溺於一去不返的過去
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.62,0:00:21.97,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}緊緊擁抱今天吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.12,0:00:28.85,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}深陷於那微笑之中　好想相伴在你的左右
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.06,0:00:36.56,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}伸出手　前方應該有什麼正等待著吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.78,0:00:42.69,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}朝著那未完結的故事　飛奔而去
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.93,0:00:47.50,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}懷著一顆真誠的心向著那千難萬險之地
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.74,0:00:51.49,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}張開心靈的翅膀
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.79,0:00:58.50,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}循環傳遞著一個訊息　幸福就存於這胸中
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.58,0:01:02.10,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}接下來的少許勇氣　儘管須以眼淚相佐
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.29,0:01:06.32,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}但這或許正是變強的契機
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.45,0:01:12.92,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}溫暖的迭句　想要永遠將這份珍重守護
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.01,0:01:16.69,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}彼此心緒交織　感受著這其中的羈絆
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.80,0:01:20.59,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}所以說沒有人是孤身隻影的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.85,0:01:29.65,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}同一片藍天下　好想將這份真情實感傳遞
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.03,0:00:00.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,--------------ed--------------
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.60,0:22:19.60,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}心の奥集めた　今日の光を持って
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.25,0:22:28.39,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}飛び込んだ未知の先　何が待ってるのかな
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.68,0:22:37.73,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}未来への共鳴　想い出に重ねれば
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.93,0:22:46.77,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}勇気になる　強さになる　一人じゃないから
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.96,0:22:49.08,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}（聴かせて）
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.17,0:22:57.70,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}明日もきっと会えるね　本当の笑顔で行こう
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.89,0:23:06.58,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}夢見る夜明けを　一緒に迎えたい
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.75,0:23:15.76,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}無限の時間よりも　瞬間を駆け抜けよう
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.01,0:23:26.96,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,500)}その夢の声いつか聴かせてね　信じてく
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.60,0:22:19.60,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}懷揣著內心深處收集好了的今天的希望
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.25,0:22:28.39,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}躍入未知的前方　那裡有什麼正等待著我們吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.68,0:22:37.73,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}若是與未來共鳴　不斷憶起今天的希望
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.93,0:22:46.77,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}就會生出勇氣　就能變得堅強　也就不再是獨自一人了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.96,0:22:49.08,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}（讓你傾聽）
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.17,0:22:57.70,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}明天也一定會與你相遇　我會帶著真誠的笑容前去
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.89,0:23:06.58,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}好想和你一起迎接夢想中的黎明
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.75,0:23:15.76,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}與其坐擁這無限的時刻　倒不如追趕那絢爛的瞬間
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.01,0:23:26.96,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,500)}相信我　總有一天會讓你傾聽那夢中的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.03,0:00:00.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,--------------正文--------------
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.49,0:01:37.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今晚吃火鍋哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.52,0:01:38.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦～
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.09,0:01:39.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.24,0:01:40.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不知怎麼回事  
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.22,0:01:43.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天肉賣的特別便宜
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.26,0:01:47.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了  夏奈
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.57,0:01:50.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像個白癡一樣更興奮一點兒如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.89,0:02:04.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就先開吃啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.99,0:02:06.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹嘛啊你  這麼突然！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.16,0:02:09.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊！別專挑肉吃啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.39,0:02:11.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那本來就是我的肉啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.96,0:02:14.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啦好啦  肉還好多呢  別吵架啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.88,0:02:19.83,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}第9碗  難以掩飾了吧？阿珍的秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.54,0:02:33.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可怕…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.24,0:02:42.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我突然覺得自己好可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.32,0:02:50.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就不能好好聽我說話嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.61,0:02:52.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.57,0:02:57.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好像有超能力了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.48,0:03:02.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.20,0:03:06.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天是炸蝦  今天是火鍋
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.87,0:03:09.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚飯吃什麼我全都夢到了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.63,0:03:11.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是預知夢啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.33,0:03:14.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉～
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.98,0:03:18.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不相信啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.98,0:03:22.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是…但你堂堂正正地說些過去的事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.41,0:03:24.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之後再說這是預知誰信啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.02,0:03:30.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那  我說對了明天晚飯吃什麼  你會相信嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.70,0:03:33.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啊  你說對了我就信
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.32,0:03:36.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就今晚  等我夢見
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.58,0:04:07.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冰冷的身體溫暖起來了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.96,0:04:09.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也進來泡吧  千秋
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.85,0:04:12.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在吃什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.56,0:04:15.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏奈  夏奈
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.29,0:04:19.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在比較忙  
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.11,0:04:22.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有事請在提示音後留言
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.68,0:04:25.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是女孩子哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.62,0:04:28.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在旁邊哦  在便利店旁邊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.99,0:04:35.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏奈  這都怪你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.99,0:04:41.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那紅色的棒子…是什麼玩意？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.44,0:04:43.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胡蘿蔔？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.31,0:04:50.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼阿珍會…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.03,0:04:53.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了  不管了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.89,0:04:58.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過  阿真那傢伙心裡到底怎麼想的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.45,0:05:04.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然一直說討厭穿女裝  但看似樂在其中啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.79,0:05:06.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用管他也行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.42,0:05:13.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,改天問問他本人吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.71,0:05:22.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後呢  那什麼預知夢怎麼樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.23,0:05:24.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很微妙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.47,0:05:28.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然我總算是記得點
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.94,0:05:30.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說不出來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.41,0:05:32.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倒也不是說不出來啦…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.34,0:05:36.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼！我就知道會這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.54,0:05:37.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,預知夢個頭啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.46,0:05:39.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你給我等一下  千秋
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.64,0:05:41.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.66,0:05:43.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有重要的事跟你說
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.65,0:05:46.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比如說  內田很討厭吃年糕
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.09,0:05:48.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？突然說什麼啊  
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.96,0:05:50.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,內田還是吃年糕的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.91,0:05:52.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啦  聽我說
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.52,0:05:54.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們假設內田討厭吃年糕
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.70,0:05:59.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓內田不斷吃她討厭的年糕的過程中漸漸喜歡上了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.74,0:06:01.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有這可能嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.67,0:06:04.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別這樣  會更討厭年糕的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.37,0:06:06.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.78,0:06:10.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過  看你用什麼方法讓她吃了  也不是沒可能
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.20,0:06:16.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受到身邊的人影響  人也會改變嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.02,0:06:18.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能變好也能變壞
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.64,0:06:20.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說自己會做什麼預知夢的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.16,0:06:22.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是身邊的人一直無視她  
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.99,0:06:25.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,時間久了也就不會再提了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.04,0:06:28.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這跟那是兩回事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.41,0:06:34.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉～預知夢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.52,0:06:37.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  突然就這麼說  嚇我一跳呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.05,0:06:41.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就覺得今天少了點兒東西
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.01,0:06:44.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天保坂學長請假了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.39,0:06:45.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉？什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.59,0:06:46.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.54,0:06:48.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.90,0:06:50.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的沒什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.47,0:06:51.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,南同學
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.92,0:06:54.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  請問有事嗎  老師
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.93,0:06:57.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能到升學指導室來一下嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.89,0:06:59.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在…嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.36,0:07:03.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,南同學  我想跟你談的其實是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.27,0:07:06.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道交換留學生吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.08,0:07:07.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.17,0:07:13.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我希望成績優秀的你能作為我們學校的代表過去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.68,0:07:15.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉？但是…我…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.27,0:07:19.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然可能有很多不便  但這是個機會哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.32,0:07:24.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趁著年輕好好見識一下這廣闊的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.76,0:07:26.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接觸各種各樣的人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.69,0:07:29.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該會對你有所幫助
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.07,0:07:48.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別無視眼前正在犯愁的朋友啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.27,0:07:51.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來你有煩惱啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.08,0:07:55.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎樣才能準確地記住自己做過的夢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.11,0:07:57.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說點兒好辦法來聽聽
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.08,0:07:59.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這…這個嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.47,0:08:03.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一醒就記下來怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.45,0:08:06.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能行！這怎麼做得到啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.53,0:08:08.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊～問了白問
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.61,0:08:10.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就別問啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.47,0:08:14.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.05,0:08:16.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多符合夏奈的個性啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.86,0:08:17.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.22,0:08:20.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得就是在說夢話罷了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.52,0:08:25.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.69,0:08:26.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…沒事兒
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.54,0:08:34.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們去倒垃圾  
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.99,0:08:37.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這段時間你要打掃好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.57,0:08:38.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.85,0:08:41.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千秋變了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.23,0:08:43.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,變了…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.17,0:08:44.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉？哪裡變了？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.79,0:08:47.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話變多了？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.04,0:08:51.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎？我主動搭話的時候她總是無視啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.07,0:08:53.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或者說是無視我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.67,0:08:57.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千秋她以前不喜歡跟別人有過多接觸呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.48,0:09:00.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿真你也變了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.47,0:09:02.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經完全是個偽娘了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.46,0:09:03.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.78,0:09:04.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的假的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.20,0:09:08.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是夏奈非要我穿
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.21,0:09:11.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外加遺傳爸爸的服務精神使然
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.45,0:09:11.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.09,0:09:13.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說真的！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.66,0:09:18.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我今天要去千秋家寫作業  羡慕吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.39,0:09:22.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏奈有沒有叫阿珍一起去？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.53,0:09:24.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有沒有呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.64,0:09:26.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作業怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.17,0:09:29.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼  你也要來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.77,0:09:33.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…今天我也可以一起去嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.96,0:09:35.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.15,0:09:38.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來  快進來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.96,0:09:39.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打擾了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.82,0:09:40.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打擾了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.94,0:09:45.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.73,0:09:47.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打擾了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.41,0:09:49.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  吉野  內田也來了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.18,0:09:53.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…好久不見
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.49,0:09:54.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰啊這是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.83,0:09:58.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你再怎麼欺負他也不會覺得有趣啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.31,0:10:00.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打擾了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.83,0:10:02.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？阿真…？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.75,0:10:04.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我得到千秋的同意了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.61,0:10:06.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天可以堂堂正正的來了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.03,0:10:08.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦～
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.63,0:10:10.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不會再受夏奈你的擺佈了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.31,0:10:15.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從媽媽那遺傳的男子氣概是絕不允許那種行為的！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.21,0:10:19.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可沒同意啊  這可是我家！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.03,0:10:20.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.29,0:10:30.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然剛到沒多久  你還是趕緊滾吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.93,0:10:32.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼這樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.78,0:10:34.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,輪不到你有異議！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.91,0:10:49.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿真
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.86,0:10:54.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏奈讓我把這個給你…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.76,0:11:00.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打擾了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.39,0:11:02.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  是阿珍啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.33,0:11:04.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是朝氣十足啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.98,0:11:07.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎  我也不明白是怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.68,0:11:24.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三號艦嚴重受損  我軍陣形已經崩潰了！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.53,0:11:28.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  出動新型機  無論如何要守住這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.91,0:11:32.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Class Copper已做好離艦準備  艦橋請指示！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.49,0:11:33.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  夏奈
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.99,0:11:35.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說  夏奈啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.31,0:11:37.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏奈
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.87,0:11:38.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.56,0:11:40.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的變裝完美嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.75,0:11:41.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.82,0:11:44.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以說  我問這身變裝完美嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.94,0:11:47.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個嘛  還算是可以啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.63,0:11:49.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒被千秋揭穿
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.77,0:11:51.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,內田知道我的事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.75,0:11:56.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那吉野呢  難不成已經被她發現了嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.21,0:11:58.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也許會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.65,0:11:59.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.44,0:12:00.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你慌個什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.23,0:12:03.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不願意被揭穿的話就別做了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.49,0:12:04.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃…但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.23,0:12:08.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這樣好像是我逼著你穿女裝似的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.20,0:12:10.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實你是自由的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.44,0:12:14.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你擁有可以自由翱翔宇宙的翅膀啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.39,0:12:17.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然搞不懂你在說什麼…總之沒問題吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.77,0:12:18.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  沒問題的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.21,0:12:20.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦…哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.40,0:12:27.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  阿珍
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.77,0:12:28.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.49,0:12:33.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿珍你是中學生嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.72,0:12:36.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該不是小學生吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.49,0:12:39.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…是的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.81,0:12:41.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼阿珍要用敬語呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.24,0:12:46.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我很微不足道
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.60,0:12:49.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然是女孩子  卻用這個自稱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.48,0:12:51.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個…是我的風格啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.38,0:12:54.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼阿珍流那麼多汗啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.90,0:12:59.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是因為…酷夏的烈日正在折磨著我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.22,0:13:02.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈哈  現在是冬天啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.55,0:13:03.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.78,0:13:06.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該不會是察覺到了吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.63,0:13:08.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦哦…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.66,0:13:09.40,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿珍真是文靜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.80,0:13:12.57,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是因為家裡教導有方…有方
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.43,0:13:11.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來吉野對阿珍有興趣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.10,0:13:33.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在看我…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.40,0:13:37.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們好  在做作業嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.47,0:13:38.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也加我一個嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.75,0:13:39.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.18,0:13:41.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？內田呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.78,0:13:43.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和修一去買東西了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.58,0:13:45.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冬馬！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.33,0:13:46.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…幹嘛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.12,0:13:50.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託你  坐在我和吉野中間  幫我抵擋她的攻勢吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.94,0:13:52.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼？怎麼了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.86,0:13:55.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從剛才她就兩眼發光地盯著我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.48,0:13:59.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是人稱「堅不可推」的吉野小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.02,0:14:02.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能已經懷疑了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.21,0:14:04.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰給的名號啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.65,0:14:05.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃…千秋吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.12,0:14:10.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽著啊  不管是不是被看穿了  
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.20,0:14:12.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之不要與她為敵
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.95,0:14:14.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是你的戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.83,0:14:16.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這…這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.47,0:14:17.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那加油吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.72,0:14:20.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等  你去哪兒？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.51,0:14:26.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們班留的作業  很可能是明天我們班要留的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.85,0:14:29.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在留作業之前做完  這就是我的戰鬥方針
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.21,0:14:32.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且千秋和吉野的中間  
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.14,0:14:36.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正是可以獲得兩側支援的絕佳戰場
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.90,0:14:39.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求你了  留在這裡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.87,0:14:42.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,煩死了！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.91,0:14:44.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.12,0:14:46.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂！別鬧了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.39,0:14:51.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼阿珍你要那麼慌張啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.76,0:14:54.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是女孩子的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.05,0:14:56.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好奇怪的阿珍
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.35,0:15:01.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我先回去啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.16,0:15:09.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行了…受不了了…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.50,0:15:13.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是時候罷手了吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.88,0:15:15.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是挺好的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.58,0:15:17.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼嘛…是夏奈啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.40,0:15:19.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我該怎麼辦好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.66,0:15:21.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,討厭的年糕也會總有一天會喜歡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.41,0:15:24.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？我喜歡吃年糕啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.16,0:15:29.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎樣  你不這麼打扮恐怕就進不了我家門啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.55,0:15:30.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.65,0:15:33.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寫完了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.33,0:15:36.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,頭腦好的湊在一塊就是做得快啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.34,0:15:39.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是覺得因為沒有笨蛋在場
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.68,0:15:41.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都回去的很早啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.81,0:15:44.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.18,0:15:45.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.70,0:15:49.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有事…要拜託千秋
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.62,0:15:53.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也想有所改變  像千秋那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.76,0:15:55.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你突然在說些什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.79,0:15:58.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我討厭被叫做原味酸奶
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.07,0:16:02.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是不喜歡吃胡蘿蔔
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.09,0:16:03.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會錯意啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.07,0:16:12.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必須去買東西了…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.16,0:16:17.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我變了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.09,0:16:19.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得是變了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.62,0:16:21.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪方面？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.06,0:16:23.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,變得愛說話了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.48,0:16:26.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒覺得自己變了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.41,0:16:28.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.25,0:16:31.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且  我不認為換個外號人就會變
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.98,0:16:32.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.21,0:16:36.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別那麼沮喪  主要還是看自己
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.64,0:16:37.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.84,0:16:40.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是修一  也是有優點的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.96,0:16:42.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉？哪方面？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.75,0:16:44.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要問哪方面嘛…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.80,0:16:48.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非要說的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.46,0:16:49.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非要說的話…？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.16,0:16:51.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.32,0:16:54.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別急啊…你頭腦不差啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.73,0:16:57.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.73,0:17:01.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道你想說笨蛋才有個性嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.59,0:17:02.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…不是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.58,0:17:13.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.53,0:17:14.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.03,0:17:16.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐躺你身邊你就無視啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.91,0:17:18.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才一億日元而已啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.76,0:17:19.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是啦  聽我說
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.52,0:17:23.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我夢見千秋你吧哩吧哩的吃胡蘿蔔條了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.66,0:17:24.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.55,0:17:27.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之後好像又吃了什麼好吃的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.96,0:17:32.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看啊  這裡剛好放著我夢見的胡蘿蔔條呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.97,0:17:34.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行了你  一邊兒去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.49,0:17:36.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來  千秋  請用吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.49,0:17:37.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕對不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.95,0:17:41.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不先吃了這個  也許就吃不到好東西了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.47,0:17:42.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你做什麼啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.30,0:17:44.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.72,0:17:53.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千秋  換洗衣服我放這裡了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.19,0:17:55.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的  春香姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.58,0:17:58.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香姐姐  那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.07,0:17:59.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.16,0:18:02.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是變了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.72,0:18:04.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了  突然這麼問
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.63,0:18:07.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天有人說我變了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.15,0:18:09.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朋友說的？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.46,0:18:10.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.32,0:18:12.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我想就是變了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.96,0:18:17.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和大家在一起會不知不覺受到影響的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.05,0:18:20.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洗完澡就來吃飯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.83,0:18:27.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不是說對了！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.59,0:18:29.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,管你對不對！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.76,0:18:31.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃螃蟹啊  要把這殼…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.98,0:18:35.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對對  要把殼這樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.41,0:18:37.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.64,0:18:43.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊…看錯了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.35,0:18:47.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我以為是胡蘿蔔條  其實是螃蟹啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.69,0:18:50.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過還是不說了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.64,0:18:57.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,螃蟹就是要安安靜靜的吃嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.14,0:19:04.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早安
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.95,0:19:06.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃…啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.82,0:19:07.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早安
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.89,0:19:09.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早安  怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.60,0:19:13.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還說怎麼了…奶油花居然…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.54,0:19:16.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奶油花？又是預知夢嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.39,0:19:17.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正你根本沒做夢吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.11,0:19:20.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做是做了  可我忘了…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.40,0:19:23.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦才好？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.07,0:19:24.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.91,0:19:26.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千秋啊  千秋
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.77,0:19:28.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是在等人吐槽嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.68,0:19:31.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…什麼都沒看見哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.81,0:19:33.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管嗎？真不管嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.95,0:19:35.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然不知道能忍到什麼時候
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.80,0:19:37.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.35,0:19:41.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們偷偷摸摸的說什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.02,0:19:46.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早安
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.17,0:19:47.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早安
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.96,0:19:49.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早…安
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.30,0:19:50.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早安…呃
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.97,0:19:52.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.01,0:19:54.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.54,0:19:57.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作業帶來了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.97,0:19:58.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作業…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.94,0:20:00.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說到作業…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.54,0:20:04.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿珍…現在在做什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.07,0:20:06.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,南家三姐妹
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.25,0:20:06.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,～再來一碗～
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.39,0:20:11.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把領帶繫緊了  保坂
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.61,0:20:12.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  老師
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.94,0:20:17.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇哇～春香為我做了便當哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.26,0:20:22.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼打我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.38,0:20:23.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼你要搶
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.38,0:20:30.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保坂啊  你不是為了讓春香吃才每天做便當的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.92,0:20:33.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然一次都沒送出
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.61,0:20:36.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想吃春香的便當嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.31,0:20:38.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是想讓春香吃你做的便當呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.08,0:20:39.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是哪個？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.84,0:20:44.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,速水前輩  今天的社團活動…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.46,0:20:46.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真希！作為參考我問問你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.38,0:20:49.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是吃的那方還是被吃的那方
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.92,0:20:50.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回答我！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.21,0:20:53.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想…應該是吃的那方
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.90,0:20:54.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.56,0:20:59.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真希  不要因為想脫身就亂說話啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.00,0:21:02.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是因為他太噁心…呃  太有魄力才…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.11,0:21:06.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說回來你真是丟臉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.40,0:21:09.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保坂  你本該是個做任何事都拼盡全力的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.30,0:21:13.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但現在的你卻迷失了自我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.11,0:21:17.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好想一想  你渴望的到底是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.63,0:21:19.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你又是什麼人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.16,0:21:22.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我到底渴望什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.25,0:21:25.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師  我到底應該怎麼做
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.81,0:21:27.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把領帶繫好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.37,0:21:28.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  老師
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.13,0:21:34.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都怪你  便當都一塌糊塗了！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.49,0:21:35.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼賠我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.70,0:21:38.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你剛才踢了我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.37,0:21:39.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,踢了又怎樣
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.89,0:21:40.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,踢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.77,0:21:44.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊…這就是答案啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.58,0:21:46.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是踢還是打
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.28,0:21:48.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吃還是被吃
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.91,0:21:50.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並不是二選一的問題
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.77,0:21:53.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我兩邊都要！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.93,0:21:55.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對  我是保坂
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.25,0:21:58.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是一塌糊塗  也照吃！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.72,0:21:59.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不給你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.50,0:23:33.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是有認為喝醋就會讓身體變軟的人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.92,0:23:36.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魚骨沾到醋確實會變軟
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.72,0:23:39.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是人骨和魚骨可不一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.24,0:23:42.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,醋會在人體內分解成炭酸和水
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.50,0:23:44.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是趁早放棄這念頭去做柔軟運動吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.26,0:23:44.97,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\an8\fad(370,0)}第10碗  「舍華求實的年紀」
